         Orocos Components Library (OCL) v0.2.1

This release of the Orocos Components Library is a bugfix
and documentation-update release. The following issues
were fixed

 o bug #276: Fixed ...-NOTFOUND Target OS flags in build system
 o bug #280: Axis Drive function contains wrong check

This release also provides the 'Component Template' package
which allows Orocos Component builders to quickly construct
a new component. The template offers a ready to use build system
(using cmake), an example component and an example test program.